## 📌 Project Overview
This repository showcases professional data analytics practices applied to an e-commerce transactional audit trace containing 1,200 unique sales rows across multiple fiscal cycles. The workflow details an explicit staging and cleaning architecture, statistical baseline profiling, and multi-dimensional reporting arrays designed to reveal consumer behavior, marketing efficacy, and supply-chain logistics.

