## 🛠️ Data Architecture & Engineering Staging

The production data lifecycle begins on the raw ingestion tab (`orignal data`) and moves through systematic validation constraints before being committed to the structured analytical model on the `CleanedData` sheet.

### Structural Transformations Applied:
1. **Sparsity Mitigation (`CouponCode`):** Replaced null fields and blank textual frames with a standardized identifier (`"NoCoupon"`). This prevents Excel's Pivot engine from clustering sparse attributes under broken `(blank)` visual headers.
2. **Feature Engineering (`IsRepeatBuyer`):** Calculated historic customer recurrence loops using deterministic evaluation array structures to derive customer status cohorts (`One-Time` vs. `Repeat Buyer`).
3. **Fulfillment Audit Mapping:** Classified order status codes (`Shipped`, `Delivered`, `Pending`, `Cancelled`, `Returned`) to serve as top-level parameters for distinguishing active operational sales from revenue losses.

### Comprehensive Staging Schema
| Attribute Field | Data Profile | Analytical Importance | Engineering Action |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `OrderID` | Text / Primary Key | Unique transaction trace identifier | Verified alphanumeric uniformity & zero duplication |
| `Date` | Temporal (YYYY-MM-DD) | Temporal anchor for tracking seasonal velocity | Coerced variant inputs into standardized ISO date format |
| `CustomerID` | Text / Alternative Key | Maps individual account purchase paths | Cross-referenced for behavioral frequency analysis |
| `Product` | Categorical String | Product portfolio segments (7 Core Skus) | Validated strings against master stock catalog labels |
| `Quantity` | Discrete Integer | Unit depth purchased per transaction | Enforced positive integer constraints ($Q > 0$) |
| `UnitPrice` | Continuous Currency | Baseline catalog price per individual unit | Standardized floating points for currency formatting |
| `PaymentMethod` | Categorical String | Transaction mechanism used by consumer | Grouped into 5 standardized checkout variations |
| `OrderStatus` | Categorical String | Operational logistical fulfillment state | Set up structural indices for return/loss tracking |
| `CouponCode` | Categorical String | Marketing campaign indicator | Imputed sparse blocks with `"NoCoupon"` flags |
| `ReferralSource` | Categorical String | User acquisition channel tracking | Isolated attribution tags for ROI reporting |
| `TotalPrice` | Continuous Currency | Aggregate gross sale volume before adjustments | Formatted to 2 decimals; flagged for margin calculation adjustments |
| `IsRepeatBuyer` | Categorical (Derived) | Engineered customer loyalty feature | Created using logic criteria based on purchase frequency |

